{"tid":1939261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自己歷史自己寫：香港人抗疫史","createTime":"2020-03-23T04:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T00:54:54.000Z","uid":206594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"766ed227a5a4628462b04ed034cf748e0b3c9f89","tid":1939261,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4QX8Kr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4QX8Kr.png&h=18bc36c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁啱立到wiki呼籲大家公正持平咁編寫武漢肺炎<br />\n入去一睇，發覺講香港嘅篇幅都歸類咗喺中國入面<br />\n仲得鬼死咁短<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Domestic responses</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E2%80%9320_coronavirus_pandemic#Domestic_responses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2019%25E2%2580%259320_coronavirus_pandemic%23Domestic_responses&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfrz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=63269ac9\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E2%80%9320_coronavirus_pandemic#Domestic_responses</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>National responses to the 2019&ndash;20 coronavirus pandemic</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_responses_to_the_2019%E2%80%9320_coronavirus_pandemic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNational_responses_to_the_2019%25E2%2580%259320_coronavirus_pandemic&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfrz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=62cc98d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_responses_to_the_2019%E2%80%9320_coronavirus_pandemic</a></span><br />\n<br />\n希望英文好啲嘅手足幫幫手<br />\n寫返part屬於香港嘅段落<br />\n公正客觀持平咁將香港人嘅自律，對政府嘅不信任，以及政府嘅無能<br />\n一一記載喺wiki上面<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有save低可靠啲嘅英文source<br />\n亦歡迎喺度share份，方便手足去mark ref"},{"pid":"8c177c3fbc192c2b336372cd4f9f45916143fa7d","tid":1939261,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"